00:12.110 --> 00:14.579
My kingdom for
an empty bench

00:14.581 --> 00:17.448
where I can devour
my cheeseburger.

00:17.450 --> 00:19.951
It's two cheeseburgers
you ordered, hotshot.

00:19.953 --> 00:23.221
It's gonna be three if
you don't finish yours.

00:24.323 --> 00:26.357
Oh, there's a spot.

00:26.359 --> 00:27.892
Hey, whoa, whoa.

00:32.764 --> 00:34.465
Huh.

00:34.467 --> 00:36.767
Excuse me, ma'am,
does this bag belong to you?

00:36.769 --> 00:37.835
No.

00:37.837 --> 00:40.605
Uh-uh. No.
No?

00:40.607 --> 00:41.739
Hey, guys,

00:41.741 --> 00:43.674
does that bag belong to any of you?
No.

00:43.676 --> 00:45.443
No?
No. Uh-uh.

00:45.445 --> 00:47.612
Sir, did you forget your bag
over here?

00:47.614 --> 00:50.514
It's not mine.
Did you guys forget... Okay.

00:50.516 --> 00:51.882
Excuse me,
anybody with this bag?

00:51.884 --> 00:54.885
This bag belong
to anyone?

