Yeah. Let's just keep it calm
and back everybody up, okay?

01:13.873 --> 01:15.906
Guys, we need you
to back up, okay?

01:15.908 --> 01:18.276
Please, folks. Folks,
will you please clear the area?

01:18.278 --> 01:21.345
Central, 12 David. Be advised,
we have a suspicious package

01:21.347 --> 01:24.248
at Union Square Park
at 14th and Broadway.

01:24.250 --> 01:27.351
Have Bomb Squad respond
at this time, please.

01:27.353 --> 01:29.320
Do you have
the appraisal?

01:29.322 --> 01:31.722
I have the appraisal.
Okay.

01:31.724 --> 01:33.791
What about the letter
from the mortgage broker?

01:33.793 --> 01:35.860
I got the letter from
the mortgage broker.

01:35.862 --> 01:37.595
Come on, stop worrying.

01:37.597 --> 01:39.297
Okay.

01:42.834 --> 01:44.568
Maybe you should have worn
your blue tie.

01:44.570 --> 01:45.503
Why?

01:45.505 --> 01:48.172
It brings out your eyes.
What?

01:48.174 --> 01:52.343
Blue implies honesty,
dependability, trust.

01:52.345 --> 01:53.577
I'm asking him

01:53.579 --> 01:55.713
to refinance our
mortgage, not marry me.

01:55.715 --> 01:57.214
I know.
I'm just nervous, that's all.

01:57.216 --> 01:58.516
Don't be nervous.
We got this

01:58.518 --> 02:00.117
in the bag, okay?
My job is secure,

02:00.119 --> 02:01.119
our credit is good,

02:01.120 --> 02:02.286
and we have been
with this bank

02:02.288 --> 02:03.654
for over 20 years.
Isn't that right?

02:03.656 --> 02:04.789
Mr. Reagan. Mrs. Reagan.

02:04.791 --> 02:06.824
Hi. How are you?
Please, right this way.

02:06.826 --> 02:07.692
All right, let's go.

02:07.694 --> 02:10.061
Relax.

02:18.136 --> 02:19.470
What is it?
What's going on?

02:19.472 --> 02:21.305
Someone left an
unattended bag.

02:21.307 --> 02:22.973
Aw, man. Is it a bomb?

02:22.975 --> 02:24.775
We're not sure
what it is yet, sir.

02:24.777 --> 02:26.310
That's why
we're checking it out.

03:13.125 --> 03:14.592
Why's everybody
laughing?

03:14.594 --> 03:16.093
It's a Spanky.

03:16.095 --> 03:17.828
What's a Spanky?

03:17.830 --> 03:19.363
The guerilla
street artist, Spanky.

03:19.365 --> 03:21.665
You've never seen
his art around town?

03:21.667 --> 03:22.833
This isn't art.

03:22.835 --> 03:24.702
This is yelling "fir""
in a packed theater.

03:24.704 --> 03:26.003
Yeah.

03:30.842 --> 03:33.911
We did everything by the
numbers with the appraisal.

03:33.913 --> 03:35.279
Mm-hmm.

03:35.281 --> 03:36.947
Even used the company
the bank recommended.

03:36.949 --> 03:40.217
Yeah. Our mortgage broker
says we're a slam dunk.

03:40.219 --> 03:42.753
Slam dunk.
Slam dunk.

03:46.124 --> 03:48.192
I'm sorry.
We're not gonna be able

03:48.194 --> 03:50.528
to refinance your mortgage
at this time.

03:50.530 --> 03:52.329
You what?
Why not?

03:52.331 --> 03:54.198
I suggest you check back
with us in a year.

03:54.200 --> 03:55.266
A year?

03:55.268 --> 03:56.700
To a year and a half.

03:56.702 --> 03:59.303
No, no, no. You hold on
to those, because

03:59.305 --> 04:00.838
there's got to be some mistake.
Okay, Danny, Danny...

04:00.840 --> 04:02.206
We got to work
this out here.

04:02.208 --> 04:03.607
You know
what my husband is

04:03.609 --> 04:05.142
really saying here
is that we have been

04:05.144 --> 04:06.544
very loyal to this bank--
20 years

04:06.546 --> 04:08.245
we've been with this bank.
Over 20 years.

04:08.247 --> 04:09.580
Yeah, so that much loyalty

04:09.582 --> 04:12.383
maybe deserves
a little bit of a reward.

04:12.385 --> 04:13.651
Big reward.

04:13.653 --> 04:15.419
We appreciate your business.

04:15.421 --> 04:19.190
We do. That's why I hope you'll
check back with us in a year.

04:19.192 --> 04:20.491
To a year and a half.

04:20.493 --> 04:22.293
- Well, I think that you...
- Listen up!

04:22.295 --> 04:24.895
Do exactly as I say
and nobody gets hurt!

04:24.897 --> 04:27.531
Everybody down
on the ground!

04:27.533 --> 04:30.367
Get down!
Everybody get down on the floor!

04:30.369 --> 04:32.336
Get on the floor!

04:33.306 --> 04:35.673
Heads down! Heads down!

04:35.675 --> 04:37.107
Everybody on the ground!

04:37.109 --> 04:38.375
Danny, get down, get d...

04:38.377 --> 04:39.743
All right.

04:39.745 --> 04:42.413
Heads down!
Get on the ground!

04:44.783 --> 04:47.384
Keep your head down!
Let me see your hands!

04:47.386 --> 04:49.753
Let me see your hands!

04:49.755 --> 04:51.555
Heads down!

04:53.825 --> 04:55.993
Bags, purses and phones!

04:55.995 --> 04:57.495
Let's go! Now!

